      <title>巴基斯坦预计今年经济增长将低于目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/pakistan-expects-economy-will-grow-slower-than-target-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦预测今年截至6月份的经济将增长2.38％，低于预算中宣布的3.5％的目标。]]></description>
